{"id":1221,"date":"2024-12-16T18:03:41","date_gmt":"2024-12-16T18:03:41","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/?page_id=1221"},"modified":"2024-12-16T18:06:36","modified_gmt":"2024-12-16T18:06:36","slug":"donottrack","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/donottrack\/","title":{"rendered":"Do Not Track"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1221\" class=\"elementor elementor-1221\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dfb086a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"dfb086a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f4f5ed e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"7f4f5ed\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a37c8ef animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a37c8ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;slideInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Hey Nosy!<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-99c0c73 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"99c0c73\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;slideInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Do Not Track<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-46ab56f elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"46ab56f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00a0<\/p><hr \/><h3>BEATiFY Do Not Track (DNT) Policy<\/h3><h4>1. Overview<\/h4><p>BEATiFY is committed to respecting your privacy and providing transparency regarding how we collect and use your information. This <strong>Do Not Track (DNT) Policy<\/strong> explains our approach to Do Not Track signals and similar technologies, as well as how we comply with user preferences and privacy standards.<\/p><h4>2. What is Do Not Track (DNT)?<\/h4><p>Do Not Track is a browser setting that allows users to signal websites and online services that they do not want to be tracked. When enabled, your browser sends a signal to websites, analytics services, and advertising networks requesting that tracking of your online activity be disabled.<\/p><h4>3. BEATiFY\u2019s Response to DNT Signals<\/h4><p>At this time, BEATiFY does not respond to Do Not Track signals. While DNT is an important privacy tool, there is no industry-standard agreement on how to interpret and respond to these signals. We continue to monitor developments in the DNT standard and will adjust our approach as industry guidelines and regulations evolve.<\/p><h4>4. How BEATiFY Protects Your Privacy<\/h4><p>Even though we do not currently respond to DNT signals, BEATiFY prioritizes your privacy through the following measures:<\/p><ul><li><strong>Minimal Data Collection<\/strong>: We only collect data necessary to provide and improve the BEATiFY Service, as outlined in our Privacy Policy.<\/li><li><strong>User Controls<\/strong>: You can manage your privacy preferences, including disabling tracking for targeted advertisements and analytics, through your <strong>BEATiFY account settings<\/strong>.<\/li><li><strong>Transparency<\/strong>: We clearly explain how we collect, use, and share your personal data in our Privacy Policy.<\/li><\/ul><h4>5. Managing Your Tracking Preferences<\/h4><p><strong>Opt-Out Options for Tracking<\/strong><br \/>While BEATiFY does not respond to DNT signals, you can take the following steps to manage tracking on our platform:<\/p><ol><li><strong>Adjust Browser Settings<\/strong>: Use your browser settings to block cookies or third-party trackers. This may affect certain features of the BEATiFY Service.<\/li><li><strong>Disable Analytics Tracking<\/strong>: You can opt out of analytics and tracking tools used by BEATiFY through your account privacy settings.<\/li><li><strong>Advertising Preferences<\/strong>: Manage your preferences for targeted advertising through the settings in your account or third-party opt-out tools such as the <strong>AdChoices program<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ol><p><strong>Note<\/strong>: Disabling certain tracking technologies may limit your access to personalized content and features.<\/p><h4>6. Third-Party Tracking<\/h4><p>Third parties, such as advertisers and analytics providers, may collect data about your interactions with the BEATiFY Service. These third parties may or may not respect Do Not Track signals. To manage their tracking:<\/p><ul><li>Review their privacy policies to understand how they process your data.<\/li><li>Use tools like <strong>browser extensions<\/strong> or <strong>ad blockers<\/strong> to control third-party tracking.<\/li><\/ul><h4>7. Future Updates<\/h4><p>BEATiFY is committed to improving user privacy and will update this policy as new technologies, regulations, and industry standards emerge. Any significant changes to this policy will be communicated via the BEATiFY Service or email.<\/p><h4>8. Contact Us<\/h4><p>If you have questions or concerns about our Do Not Track Policy, please contact us:<\/p><p><strong>Email<\/strong>: <a href=\"mailto:privacy@beatifyaudio.com\">privacy@beatifyaudio.com<\/a><br \/><strong>Mail<\/strong>:<br \/><strong>BEATiFY Group Inc.<\/strong><br \/>92 Caplan Dr<br \/>Barrie, ON L9SLV1<\/p><hr \/><p>\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Hey Nosy! Do Not Track \u00a0 BEATiFY Do Not Track (DNT) Policy 1. Overview BEATiFY is committed to respecting your privacy and providing transparency regarding how we collect and use your information. This Do Not Track (DNT) Policy explains our approach to Do Not Track signals and similar technologies, as well as how we comply [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-1221","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1221","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1221"}],"version-history":[{"count":5,"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1221\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1227,"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/1221\/revisions\/1227"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/beatifygroup.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1221"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}